    "SummaryEnglish": "Shenmo Cemetery, resting place of ancient Gods and Demons. An inconspicuous grave, surrounded by the tombs of giants, lies at the side. Suddenly, a young man emerges from the grave. Chen Nan, who had last felt the embrace of death, finds himself surrounded by the graves of Deities whose names shook the old Xiuhuan and Mohuan Continents. What happened to them? Why was he buried here as well? He finds that ten thousand years has passed, and the world has changed much in the meantime.(novel update)",
